  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this research study is to see how helpful two different interventions offered
      through the Calmer Life program are in reducing worry and improving mood. The investigators
      also want to understand how a program like Calmer Life can be offered in underserved
      communities.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
